data.description: INVESTORS are you ready for your next rental or flip in quiet neighborhood?  Tenant just left and property has received many upgrades sitting on .74 of an acre!  New Septic system was installed this year and recent updates include: Metal Roof, Hot Water Heater, Dishwasher and Living Room Ceiling Fan to name a few.  This property has a fenced back yard and large oversized lot allow for ample space for hobbies and outdoor play!House is being sold as is and seller is not open to repairs.
